Publicado em 28 May 2019

Participation in the Autumn Meeting of the Brazilian Society of Physics.

Luiz T. F. Eleno and Igor Hideki presented work at the 2019 autumn meeting of the Brazilian Society of Physics, showing ComputEEL/MatSci results on materials properties and superconductivity.
